xt":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/umar-burden-long-salat-lectures\/","url_meta":{"origin":28829,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Sermons: Do not burden people with long prayers, lectures","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Adi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cO people, do not make Allah hateful to his servants.\u201d They said, \u201cHow is that? Allah correct you!\u201d Umar said, \u201cOne of you is an Imam and he prolongs the prayer for people until what is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7672,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/dua-prophet-rain-miracle\/","url_meta":{"origin":28829,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Miracles: The Prophet prays for rain, it rains","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, on Friday while he was delivering a sermon in Medina. The man said, \u201cThere is no rain, so please call upon your Lord to bless us with rain.\u201d The Prophet looked at the sky\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19144,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/13\/mercy-unity-punishment-division\/","url_meta":{"origin":28829,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Unity: Mercy in unity, punishment in division","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said upon the pulpit, \u201cWhoever is not grateful for small things will not be grateful for large things. Whoever is not thankful to people is not thankful to Allah. Mentioning the blessings of Allah is gratitude,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15805,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/friday-jumuah-heedless\/","url_meta":{"origin":28829,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Neglecting Friday prayer leads to hard heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said while upon his wooden pulpit, \u201cPeople need to stop neglecting the Friday prayers, lest Allah place a seal over their hearts and then they become heedless.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 865 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34642,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/umar-greed-is-poverty\/","url_meta":{"origin":28829,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Greed: Greed is poverty and slavery to materialism","autho